f a number) shares a Greatest Common Divisor that&amp;#x27;s &amp;gt;= 2.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;comment&#34;&gt;*/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;    &lt;span class=&#34;type&#34;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;variable&#34;&gt;hcf&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;operator&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;number&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;    &lt;span class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span class=&#34;type&#34;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; i: freq.keySet())&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;        hcf = gcd(hcf, freq.get(i));&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;    &lt;span class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; hcf &amp;gt; &lt;span class=&#34;number&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&amp;#125;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;private&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;type&#34;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title function_&#34;&gt;gcd&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;params&#34;&gt;(&lt;span class=&#34;type&#34;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; x, &lt;span class=&#34;type&#34;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; y)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&amp;#123;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;    &lt;span class=&#34;type&#34;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;variable&#34;&gt;temp&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;operator&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;number&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;    &lt;span class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;while&lt;/span&gt; (y != &lt;span class=&#34;numb